Ooops.

Good thing I use F5 a lot.

Is this one of those "Spot the differences" kind of games, or do you actually want help? If the latter, we'll need more than a picture with at least 3 things different than the stock game's menu screen.

Ahhhh! Minmus is going to collide with us !!!

Look, in the lower left! The kraken egg is hatching! The resulting gravitational distortion waves are causing tidal forces strong enough stretch Kerbin itself into a non-spherical shape! WE ARE UTTERLY DOOMED

This has drifted far from the topic (I think, the topic is vague). Closed.
